  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.BdhVFmTGhjLm1Ceo]{Channel Divinity} to exude a terrifying presence. As an action, you force each creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you to make a <strong>Wisdom saving throw</strong>. On a failed save, a creature becomes <strong>frightened </strong>of you for 1 minute. The frightened creature can repeat this saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: When you add this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Channel Divinity.</em></p>\n</section>",
